{"tid":1424156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩種「光復香港，時代革命」","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:10:27.000Z","uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"22f28bf414c9b85113c0771fbe3c777dae455929","tid":1424156,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"甲：提出者：許翰文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgjEon5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgjEon5.png&h=057f688b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連登解釋：<br />\n爭取雙普選<br />\n永續基本法<br />\n唔要港獨本民青<br />\n<br />\n乙：提出者：梁天琦、青政<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oa6Z7QK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOa6Z7QK.png&h=169ff891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方解釋：<br />\n爭取港人應有權利<br />\n革新追上時代步伐<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youngspiration/1763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyoungspiration%2F1763&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnTeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=7b3fa414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youngspiration/1763</a><br />\n<br />\n連登解釋：<br />\n教條主義<br />\n老屎忽<br />\n天琦唔會咁諗<br />\n陳浩天唔係咁諗<br />\n青政係鬼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家分清楚<br />\n兩者完全唔同<br />\n無任何關係"},{"pid":"16b700afd7355bcf74f165102d6fd58284d1d043","tid":1424156,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"重溫 616, 71, 721 宣言, 文宣請加油, 令我們的行動合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423473</a><br />\n<br />\n其中一個方向係<br />\n正名「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n光復香港 = 回復以往繁榮既香港<br />\n方法: 首4大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n<br />\n時代革命=香港體制要改革<br />\n方法: 第五大訴求<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n而唔係林鄭所誤解既港獨<br />\n<br />\n建議之一, 請其他巴打更改"}]}